[160.323597, "o", "The model has strong predictive capabilities (clean AUC-ROC of 0.8861) and should definitely be deployed. However, to prevent swamping the fraud operations team and leaking millions in unreviewed alerts, the engineering team must set the production classification threshold to exactly 0.63. We recommend monitoring daily alert volumes post-deployment to ensure they remain within the 1,500 daily limit as transaction volume fluctuates.\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h> EOF\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r"]
